Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们梦想着  改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}杂音中  传来你的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭开我  欢笑之下的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐着  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们渴求着前往未来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却为此在过去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑着的此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:28.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…永遠普遍の愛なんて　信じられるのかしら？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:35.02,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い紅茶に溶かす　ため息模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:39.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　待ちくたびれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:48.01,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを追いかけて　堕ちるワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:52.39,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまで行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}イロトリドリの闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:23:02.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道標の旋律　心が騒ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時計仕掛けの運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:09.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊してしまえ　私は自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:13.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが真実
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:21.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze　生きる証
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:28.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…是否能相信  所谓永恒的爱？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:35.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叹息溶化于甘美红茶  化为波纹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:39.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已经  再也按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:48.01,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追寻着你  坠落往  Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:52.39,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何处才是尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}穿越色彩斑斓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:23:02.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指明前路的旋律  踊动不已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假使命运如时钟般不可逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:09.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破坏它  我将获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:13.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是唯一的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:21.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze  是我生存的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵体受到的伤害  会传递给契约者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  杀掉灵体的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  艾莉丝  不要再攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是…那孩子的…菲利浦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我刀刃相向的罪  就用你的死来偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了吗  我已经没法阻止艾莉丝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回想起来吧  你的话一定能阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那个资格…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手  艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量…被抑制住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  都说你能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:38.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重叠的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…我爸爸出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…三天前出门到现在都没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样的事  以前也经常有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…会平安回来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不想变成一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利浦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你爸爸带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子能以那种笑脸  谈论着爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸陪我的时间变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还能那样想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…要做这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要和灵体订下契约啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有菲利浦在了  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要和灵体订下契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为了菲利浦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了菲利浦才想改变过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候…如果没在那契约书上签字的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家族也就不会走向没落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有相信那个庸医的话  妻子就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没相信那帮家伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会落得现在这种悲惨的境地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够重来一次的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让菲利浦得到幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做哪里有错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是…为了菲利浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我儿子才杀人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是一个人…也就无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但菲利浦还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有义务要让那孩子得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像现在这样的话…菲利浦只会变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受那种事  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了  我是他的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了菲利浦  我什么事都做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本什么都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才懒得管你那些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你没能陪在菲利浦的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不去陪在菲利浦身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是你的儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你却…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想变成一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是他的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔巴特在地下室里反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷也不可以外出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷是这样吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我一个人  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有必要去改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子只要有人能对他说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没关系住在这里也不错」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能陪在他身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样  菲利浦就会感到很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利浦也有一张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥…奥兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹  可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少和那孩子再…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少和那孩子再…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  菲利浦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是菲利浦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的是我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到他差点就要被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且那男人已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了活着堕入阿比斯或者死  别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉我主  文森特大人之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来带那孩子回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文斯  你来时乘坐的马车还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让奥兹去安全的地方休息  马车借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  基尔  我得去找菲利浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是基尔的请求  我都会照办的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜来打扰  真是抱歉  雷因兹华斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为基尔闹别扭  说他不想回奈特雷家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…我们就先告辞了  艾可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然很想和基尔好好聊聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还要去善后处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我和基尔不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你到门口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请您路上小心了  文森特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是对你一如既往地冷淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  太不坦率了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛  那爱害羞的性格也正是他可爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚  基尔的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们有着血缘这层羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护主人是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那家伙却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾惜自身的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很关心奥兹大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你目前该做的  是别的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你自己的事  还没和他说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够重来一次的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让菲利浦得到幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了菲利浦  我什么事都做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了儿子  以这种理由去杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但父亲…就是这样的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种孩子  要是没生下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…如果说你不需要我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我为什么会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底应该存在于哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须一个人活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来绝对不想让菲利浦拥有和我一样的经历的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微让我吃惊了一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你  也会那样子生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能陪在他身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…生气了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗  感觉就像变了个人一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不明白自己都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明对那孩子…对菲利浦说过「会把爸爸带回来的」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果什么都没做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没有办法能救那个男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海藻头不是也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就别再管这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我没能遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是放不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到那孩子现在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人等待着父亲回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  完全无法理解是什么让你如此烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人是会觉得冷的  这我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我这个灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能够明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是在伤心  让那小鬼感到很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你那身衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备去潘多拉吗  这个时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有点事情想要调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这只是我个人的推测…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的「虫」逃亡事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉内部可能有人在幕后操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是害怕「虫」会泄漏什么情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让人认为是内部人员所为  故意把他放走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  在不为人知的地方消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是装作意外事故  把他杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救小孩子  没办法才杀掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的事为借口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织内竟然会有那种叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙真的存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一定会把他逼上绝路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是…值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你只要利用我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如果还能取回那片光明的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}沉浸在伤感中  也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那样只会看不到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}背叛少爷这种事  我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所有的点都联系起来--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不久  就会向着同一处聚集……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  被引向堕落的乌鸦